<h4 style="color: #DAA520;">Patch 37 (October 21, 2014)</h4><ul><li><b>Desaturate (E)</b></li><ul><li> Fixed a bug which allowed this ability to reset basic attacks on her target.</li></ul></ul><h4 style="color: #DAA520;">Patch 35 (September 11, 2014)</h4><ul><li><b>Muse (W)</b></li><ul><li> The tooltip of this ability has been updated.</li></ul></ul><h4 style="color: #DAA520;">Closed Beta: Patch 27 (March 17, 2014)</h4><ul><li>Desaturate (E)</li><ul><li>The base silence duration of this ability has been reduced to 1.0 seconds, down from 1.25.</li></ul></ul><h4 style="color: #DAA520;">Closed Beta: Patch 26 (Feb 24, 2014)</h4><ul><li>Spatter (Q)</li><ul><li>The displayed range of this ability has been updated to 1000, from previous value of 1050.</li><li>The base damage of this ability has been reduced to 65/110/155/200/245, down from 75/120/165/210/255.</li><li>The Power ratio of this ability has been reduced to 0.55, down from 0.65.</li></ul><li>Muse (W)</li><ul><li>The displayed range of this ability has been updated to 700, from previous value of 750.</li></ul><li>Desaturate (E)</li><ul><li>The displayed range of this ability has been updated to 600, from previous value of 665.</li><li>The Power ratio of this ability has been reduced to 0.6, down from 0.7.</li></ul><li>Prismatic Vortex (R)</li><ul><li>The displayed range of this ability has been updated to 800, from previous value of 875.</li></ul></ul><h4 style="color: #DAA520;">Closed Beta: Patch 10 (August 23, 2013)</h4><ul><li>Zeri's Recommended Items have been updated.</li></ul><h4 style="color: #DAA520;">Closed Beta: Patch 7 (August 02, 2013)</h4><ul><li><B>Muse (W)</B></li><ul><li>The stats gained by an ally affected by this ability has been reduced to 25% of Zeri's bonus Power, Haste, Lifedrain, Armor and Magic Resist, down from 35%.</li></ul></ul><h4 style="color: #DAA520;">Closed Beta: Patch 5 (July 18, 2013)</h4><ul><li><B>Splatter (Q)</B></li><ul><li>The base damage of this ability has been reduced to 75/120/165/210/255, down from 80/130/180/230/280.</li></ul></ul><h4 style="color: #DAA520;">Closed Beta: Patch 3 (June 21, 2013)</h4><ul><li><B>Prismatic Vortex (R)</B></li><ul><li>Bonus Health Power ratio has been reduced to 1.15, down from 1.5. Power drained from nearby shapers during the duration of Prismatic Vortex reduced to 10/15/20 per shaper, down from 10/20/30 per shaper. The Power drained from non-shapers during the duration of Prismatic Vortex has been changed to 3/4/5, adjusted from 2/4/6. Fixed a bug where Zeri would turn in a random direction if she cast Prismatic Vortex on herself.</li></ul></ul>